query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 0 AND q.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('asp.net-mvc-3',
'asynchronous',
'callback',
'character-encoding',
'console',
'grails',
'multithreading',
'nlp',
'query-optimization',
'selenium',
'selenium-webdriver');
